body:
Here is the documentation for `tf.unpack`:
https://www.tensorflow.org/versions/r0.11/api_docs/python/array_ops.html#unpack

Note this line in particular:
If num is not specified (the default), it is inferred from value's shape

Try changing your code above to just the following:

```
  tf.unpack(inputs)
```
